  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The power <span class=\"italic\">P</span> produced by a machine is represented by the equation above, where <span class=\"italic\">W</span> is the work performed during an amount of time <span class=\"italic\">t</span>. Which of the following correctly expresses <span class=\"italic\">W</span> in terms of <span class=\"italic\">P</span> and <span class=\"italic\">t</span> ?</p>\n",
